## Data Flow in Demos

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Page as Demo Page
    participant Hook as useDemoState
    participant Engine as Demo Engine
    participant Pipeline as ExtractionPipeline
    participant Timeline as MemoryTimeline

    User->>Page: Type message
    Page->>Hook: Update input state
    
    User->>Page: Send message
    Hook->>Engine: calculateContextBudget()
    Engine-->>Hook: Budget data
    
    Hook->>Pipeline: startExtraction()
    
    loop Extraction Stages
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Extract ACUs
        Pipeline->>Timeline: Update progress
        Pipeline->>Page: Stage update
    end
    
    Pipeline->>Hook: Extraction complete
    Hook->>Timeline: Render memories
    
    User->>Timeline: Click memory
    Timeline->>Page: Show details
    Page->>User: Display ACU details
```

